    b frown_blushing_sweating: Think I got the calzones to go teeth-a-teeth with H.M. herself?
    
    * *     [Not very impressive of him] How surprising, you've never seen him admit weakness to date.
    
        And before his adoring protégé, no less.
        
    * *     That's reasonable.[..] Even the most suave, dastardly scoundrel wouldn't stand a chance against a singular, ill-tempered, glorified librarian.
    
        Quite an opinion you have there, honey. You are so very confident to address her in such a manner.
        
